OL,3,CReview reveals Jersey Hospital
OL,4,CPharmacy staff feel 'dismissed'
OL,6,FThe report carried out in June,
OL,7,Frevealed the culture and behaviours of
OL,8,Fstaff in the department were
OL,9,Fconsistent themes raised by employees.
OL,11,FStaff were found to be dedicated,
OL,12,Fhonest and open in communication,
OL,13,Fhowever, some staff showed signs of
OL,14,Fbeing upset and angry at the previous
OL,15,Fand current positions including with
OL,16,Fleadership teams.
OL,18,FWithin the findings, staff reported
OL,19,Fthat education and training were often
OL,20,Frestricted by daily service pressures.
