OL,3,CReview reveals Jersey Hospital
OL,4,CPharmacy staff feel 'dismissed'
OL,6,FIt uncovered a failure to recognize
OL,7,Fthe efforts of the pharmacy team and
OL,8,Findividual members.
OL,10,FFurthermore, it has come to light that
OL,11,Fcertain staff members have access to
OL,12,Fconfidential information about their
OL,13,Fcolleagues without a valid need for
OL,14,Fsuch sensitive details.
OL,16,FEmployees further revealed they felt
OL,17,Fthere was an overall lack of
OL,18,Fcommunication and poor visibility of
OL,19,Fsenior leaders within the department.
